		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->
<ol id="sensei-quiz-list" class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>What is the importance of hosting for website speed?<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Hosting affects the connection time and resource delivery speed</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Hosting determines the design and layout of a website</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Hosting impacts the number of plugins that can be used</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list --></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Largest Contentful Paint (LCP)<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>is a new addition to the list that measures how long it takes for the page to respond to user interactions (clicks, taps, and keyboard inputs).</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>measures how much the elements on the page shift while the page is loading.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>measures when the largest element on the page becomes visible.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list --></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>What is the main goal of optimizing a website?<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Providing the best experience for visitors</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Increasing revenue</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Improving search engine rankings</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list --></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>How to test your site. Select all that apply<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>PageSpeed Insights</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>WebPageTest</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Feedback from site visitors</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Use a CDN</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list --></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>What are the three metrics known as Core Web Vitals?<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>PageSpeed Insights, WebPageTest, Performance Lab</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>First Contentful Paint (FCP), Total Blocking Time (TBT), Time to First Byte (TTFB)</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Largest Contentful Paint (LCP), Cumulative Layout Shift (CLS), Interaction to Next Paint (INP)</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list --></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->]]></content:encoded>
